OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudier from the west overnight which
OL,7,Fmay produce some spots of rain at
OL,8,Ftimes, especially across the Welsh
OL,9,Fhills. Winds stay light but a mild
OL,10,Fnight for many.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,13,Fweekend but lifting and breaking
OL,14,Fthrough the morning to leave plenty of
OL,15,Fbright and sunny spells, mostly in the
OL,16,Fsouth. Light winds and feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
